  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f30b0fa9f282556b7f5f56d224f41ba9.avif?t=1742499588\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"YUKOMON - An Indie Dream with a Greater Purpose\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"In YUKOMON, your mission is to save Juju, a little girl turned into a monster after an accident. Capture 200 unique Yukomons and face Team T, a dark force dreaming of a monster-only world, using the Yukotrix — an ancient artifact full of secrets. Crafted by a solo developer, this RPG is more than a game: it’s a personal effort to support my family through tough times.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why play?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200+ hand-drawn monsters: No duplicates, evolve your favorites with genetic bases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique battles: Cheer for your Yukomon to grant buffs and turn the tide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120+ vibrant maps: Explore with skate, kayak, fishing, and farming, under dynamic day, night, and weather.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heartfelt story: Protect Juju and defeat Team T from the DeChamps Corporation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheat Mode: Become the villain with absolute power — but the hero shines brighter.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"With retro art, a Yukopedia, and partial translations (English, Portuguese, Chinese, Russian, Japanese — names in English for aesthetics), YUKOMON is an indie with soul. Every purchase helps make a difference for me and those I love.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"YUKOMON brings a unique and innovative PET battle system: now the trainer actively joins the fight, CHEERING for their Yukomon, granting BUFFS to their partner as a boost to battle.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"In the interface, we took the liberty of partially translating, keeping ability names, characters, Yukomons, and places in English for aesthetics, so it’s not listed as fully translated on Steam.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/42a33f64fa028dfb14b73e95b396ae8d.avif?t=1742499588\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras_big/42a33f64fa028dfb14b73e95b396ae8d.avif?t=1742499588 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f30b0fa9f282556b7f5f56d224f41ba9.avif?t=1742499588\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"YUKOMON - An Indie Dream with a Greater Purpose\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"In YUKOMON, your mission is to save Juju, a little girl turned into a monster after an accident. Capture 200 unique Yukomons and face Team T, a dark force dreaming of a monster-only world, using the Yukotrix — an ancient artifact full of secrets. Crafted by a solo developer, this RPG is more than a game: it’s a personal effort to support my family through tough times.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6a79342fcff8686a2050d2ae5626b72.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Why play?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200+ hand-drawn monsters: No duplicates, evolve your favorites with genetic bases.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique battles: Cheer for your Yukomon to grant buffs and turn the tide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >120+ vibrant maps: Explore with skate, kayak, fishing, and farming, under dynamic day, night, and weather.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heartfelt story: Protect Juju and defeat Team T from the DeChamps Corporation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheat Mode: Become the villain with absolute power — but the hero shines brighter.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6f4749f021621cbdfeac6445ed1a717.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"With retro art, a Yukopedia, and partial translations (English, Portuguese, Chinese, Russian, Japanese — names in English for aesthetics), YUKOMON is an indie with soul. Every purchase helps make a difference for me and those I love.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.poster.avif?t=1742499588\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.webm?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/f6687bf3c3afe3320d7c8144901dad47.mp4?t=1742499588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"YUKOMON brings a unique and innovative PET battle system: now the trainer actively joins the fight, CHEERING for their Yukomon, granting BUFFS to their partner as a boost to battle.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"In the interface, we took the liberty of partially translating, keeping ability names, characters, Yukomons, and places in English for aesthetics, so it’s not listed as fully translated on Steam.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras/42a33f64fa028dfb14b73e95b396ae8d.avif?t=1742499588\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3537730/extras_big/42a33f64fa028dfb14b73e95b396ae8d.avif?t=1742499588 width=800 height=258 /></span></p>",
